title: Charming house for rent on a quiet street!
posting_body: ['UTILITIES INCLUDED', 'Charming house on a quiet street!', '**Flexible move-in date: August/Early September **', '**Semi-furnished=books (seen in photos), one porch sofa, one kitchen love seat, one queen bedframe in master bedroom (cannot be moved), one twin bedframe, vintage vanities in both bedrooms, deck furniture, owner storage in basement...all other furniture in photos are NOT included in the rental (better pictures to come)', 'Two bedrooms (one large, one small), semi-furnished, one and a half bath, cozy living room, spacious kitchen, beautiful sun-room, porch, deck, and sprawling yard.', 'Small pets allowed.', 'Washer/dryer on premises.', 'Street parking available with permit (included with rent), there are always parking spots available in front of the house-it is a small and quiet neighborhood.', 'Walking distance from St. Thomas campus and major St. Paul bus routes.', 'Blocks from the river.', 'Wonderful neighbors!', 'Looking for mature, clean professionals.', 'Two person limit.', 'Small dogs allowed, Cats allowed.', '$50 non-refundable pet fee.', 'No Smoking inside the home', 'Please note: there is no central air and the windows cannot support a window unit.']
